75, "no_speech_prob": 0.00313233258202672}, {"id": 51, "seek": 8912, "start": 102.64, "end": 105.88000000000001, "text": " follicles and encourage Rapunzel, baby.", "tokens": [51039, 22752, 2983, 290, 7898, 12281, 403, 17396, 11, 5156, 13, 51201], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1939256510157494, "compression_ratio": 1.74375, "no_speech_prob": 0.00313233258202672}, {"id": 52, "seek": 8912, "start": 105.88000000000001, "end": 108.12, "text": " And no, this doesn't hurt, it feels really nice.", "tokens": [51201, 843, 645, 11, 428, 1595, 470, 5938, 11, 340, 5300, 1107, 3621, 13, 51313], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1939256510157494, "compression_ratio": 1.74375, "no_speech_prob": 0.00313233258202672}, {"id": 53, "seek": 8912, "start": 108.12, "end": 109.44, "text": " And then after you scalp massaging,", "tokens": [51313, 843, 788, 706, 345, 39287, 2347, 3039, 11, 51379], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1939256510157494, "compression_ratio": 1.74375, "no_speech_prob": 0.00313233258202672}, {"id": 54, "seek": 8912, "start": 109.44, "end": 111.04, "text": " I'm going back in with my flexi-fly.", "tokens": [51379, 314, 1101, 1016, 736, 287, 351, 616, 7059, 72, 12, 12254, 13, 51459], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1939256510157494, "compression_ratio": 1.74375, "no_speech_prob": 0.00313233258202672}, {"id": 55, "seek": 8912, "start": 111.04, "end": 112.92, "text": " I wouldn't recommend doing this with any other hair brush.", "tokens": [51459, 314, 3636, 470, 4313, 1804, 428, 351, 597, 584, 4190, 14093, 13, 51553], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1939256510157494, "compression_ratio": 1.74375, "no_speech_prob": 0.00313233258202672}, {"id": 56, "seek": 8912, "start": 112.92, "end": 114.92, "text": " It's just because this has got a specific design", "tokens": [51553, 632, 338, 655, 780, 428, 468, 1392, 257, 2176, 1486, 51653], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1939256510157494, "compression_ratio": 1.74375, "no_speech_prob": 0.00313233258202672}, {"id": 57, "seek": 8912, "start": 114.92, "end": 116.68, "text": " that is not gonna cause damage of my hair.", "tokens": [51653, 326, 318, 407, 8066, 2728, 2465, 286, 616, 4190, 13, 51741], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1939256510157494, "compression_ratio": 1.74375, "no_speech_prob": 0.00313233258202672}, {"id": 58, "seek": 8912, "start": 116.68, "end": 118.24000000000001, "text": " But basically, I'm gonna brush my hair", "tokens": [51741, 887, 6209, 11, 314, 1101, 8066, 14093, 616, 4190, 51819], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.1939256510157494, "compression_ratio": 1.74375, "no_speech_prob": 0.00313233258202672}, {"id": 59, "seek": 11824, "start": 118.24, "end": 120.39999999999999, "text": " and put it in like a loose pony,", "tokens": [50363, 290, 1234, 340, 287, 588, 257, 9155, 26902, 11, 50471], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 60, "seek": 11824, "start": 120.39999999999999, "end": 123.03999999999999, "text": " just to let this oil settle for a good few hours.", "tokens": [50471, 655, 284, 1309, 428, 3056, 12259, 329, 257, 922, 1178, 2250, 13, 50603], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 61, "seek": 11824, "start": 123.03999999999999, "end": 123.88, "text": " And then like I say,", "tokens": [50603, 843, 788, 588, 314, 910, 11, 50645], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 62, "seek": 11824, "start": 123.88, "end": 126.03999999999999, "text": " I'm just gonna leave this in my hair for a few hours", "tokens": [50645, 314, 1101, 655, 8066, 2666, 428, 287, 616, 4190, 329, 257, 1178, 2250, 50753], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 63, "seek": 11824, "start": 126.03999999999999, "end": 127.36, "text": " before washing out.", "tokens": [50753, 878, 20518, 503, 13, 50819], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 64, "seek": 11824, "start": 127.36, "end": 129.0, "text": " My tips for when washing it out,", "tokens": [50819, 2011, 9040, 329, 618, 20518, 340, 503, 11, 50901], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 65, "seek": 11824, "start": 129.0, "end": 129.92, "text": " the best thing to do is use", "tokens": [50901, 262, 1266, 1517, 284, 466, 318, 779, 50947], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 66, "seek": 11824, "start": 129.92, "end": 132.2, "text": " the salt-free growth shampoo and conditioner range,", "tokens": [50947, 262, 8268, 12, 5787, 3349, 47259, 290, 4006, 263, 2837, 11, 51061], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 67, "seek": 11824, "start": 132.2, "end": 133.44, "text": " because I feel like it just makes my hair", "tokens": [51061, 780, 314, 1254, 588, 340, 655, 1838, 616, 4190, 51123], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 68, "seek": 11824, "start": 133.44, "end": 136.44, "text": " feel squeaky, squeaky clean without stripping it at all.", "tokens": [51123, 1254, 35776, 15492, 11, 35776, 15492, 3424, 1231, 37727, 340, 379, 477, 13, 51273], "temperature": 0.0, "avg_logprob": -0.14208194732666016, "compression_ratio": 1.873994638069705, "no_speech_prob": 0.006087969988584518}, {"id": 69, "seek": 11824, "start": 136.44, "end": 138.5